# Data sources
# CSV source files and Python build scripts are now TRACKED (2026-04-15):
# the data/ folder is the only backup Andy has for these, and Drupal delivery
# depends on columns like BadgePressReleaseUrl that live in the CSV source,
# not in the regenerated measures.json. Keep XLSX workbooks local (binary,
# some contain not-yet-cleared content) and local-only working notes (*.md).
data/*.xlsx
data/*.md

